# ✊✋✌️ Rock Paper Scissors Game

A fun and interactive Rock Paper Scissors game built using **HTML, CSS, and JavaScript**. Challenge the computer, track scores, and enjoy a responsive and user-friendly interface.

---

## 🚀 Features

- 🎮 Play Rock, Paper, Scissors against the computer
- 🤖 Random computer choices
- 🏆 Real-time score tracking
- 📊 Display of game results
- 🎨 Modern and responsive UI
- ⚡ Fast and interactive gameplay
- 📱 Mobile-friendly design

---

## 🛠️ Technologies Used

- HTML5
- CSS3
- JavaScript (ES6)

---

## 📂 Project Structure

```text
Rock-Paper-Scissors/
│
├── index.html
├── style.css
├── script.js
├── images/
└── README.md
```

---

## 🎮 How to Play

1. Select Rock, Paper, or Scissors.
2. The computer will randomly make its choice.
3. The winner is determined using the game rules:
   - Rock beats Scissors
   - Scissors beats Paper
   - Paper beats Rock
4. Scores update automatically after each round.

