---

## 🏆 Winning Rules

| Player Choice | Computer Choice | Result |
|--------------|----------------|---------|
| Rock | Scissors | Win |
| Rock | Paper | Lose |
| Paper | Rock | Win |
| Paper | Scissors | Lose |
| Scissors | Paper | Win |
| Scissors | Rock | Lose |

---

## 🚀 Installation

Clone the repository:

```bash
git clone https://github.com/hasnain670-web/Rock-Paper-Scissors-Game.git
```

Navigate to the project folder:

```bash
cd rock-paper-scissors
```

Open:

```text
index.html
```

in your browser.

